# TentaCLAW OS — SSH Server Configuration
# Permit root login for initial setup (change after first login)

Port 22
AddressFamily any
ListenAddress 0.0.0.0
ListenAddress ::

# Authentication
PermitRootLogin yes
PubkeyAuthentication yes
PasswordAuthentication yes
PermitEmptyPasswords no
ChallengeResponseAuthentication no

# Security
X11Forwarding no
PrintMotd no
AcceptEnv LANG LC_*
Subsystem sftp /usr/lib/openssh/sftp-server

# Logging
SyslogFacility AUTH
LogLevel INFO
